<item>
            <title>[CXF-7097] [CDI] application leaks a creational context</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-7097</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;JAXRS application are not CDI beans but that&apos;s the way CXF CDI integration gets the application - this is a nice feature.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It implies the application will rarely be normal-scope so it needs to release its creational context created at org.apache.cxf.cdi.JAXRSCdiResourceExtension#load&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This should be done in BeforeShutdown container event I think.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
